Package: warprrr
Title: S7-Powered Data Import, Wrangling, and Caching Framework
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-01-09
Authors@R:
    person("Anirban", "Shaw", , "anirbanshaw24@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4021-513X"))
Description: Provides an extensible S7 class and utility functions for
    efficient and reproducible data loading and caching.  Supports
    streamlined reading of common biomedical and tabular file formats,
    with flexible argument passing to backend readers ('data.table',
    'haven', 'arrow'). Implements automatic file/directory validation and
    file-type-based selection, plus transparent caching in Feather format
    for rapid future access. Designed to optimize clinical reporting, E2E
    data workflows, and reproducible analysis pipelinesâ€”especially in
    high-volume environments.  Includes precise evaluation timing and
    verbose messaging for workflow monitoring.  For more information, see
    <https://anirbanshaw24.github.io/warprrr/>.
